## Explanation of Dashboard Layout

The dashboard is designed for real-time monitoring of three different sensor values: temperature, humidity, and light. The panels make it easier to observe the current readings and monitor changes visually.

## Reflection Question

### Why do we separate each sensor into a different MQTT topic?

Each sensor is placed in a separate MQTT topic so that its data can be tracked, monitored, and handled independently. This also makes the system more flexible and easier to manage when adding more sensors or processing each data stream separately.
